    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-25T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-25T13:00:00-05:00" n="317"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d317">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72/12341: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Sharp</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-25T18:00:00+00:00"
                            >November 25, 1918—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received November 25—3:05 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>6003. Following joint telegram received from the Allied Ministers at Jassy dated
                    November 21st, 1918: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Urgent. The national committee of Dobroudja has sent us an address
                            asking our intervention with our Governments in order to hasten the
                            departure of Bulgarian troops and authorities in Dobroudja in order to
                            render possible the return to their homes of the population now taking
                            refuge in Moldavia and in Bessarabia where they are deprived of means of
                            existence and of shelter.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sharp</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
